{"tid":2229927,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屯門至馬鞍山單車徑啟用第四天即發生嚴重意外","createTime":"2020-10-04T16:31:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-04T18:51:42.000Z","uid":253829,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"766499eb1d4e4b4aa1ed12dd627d953d5c3932e2","tid":2229927,"uid":253829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T16:31:24.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】屯門至馬鞍山單車徑元朗至上水段啟用第四天發生嚴重意外。一家四口昨早到單車徑踏單車，途經元朗錦綉花園大道近錦壆路一條行人隧道落斜時，母親疑失控撞向路中膠柱，再衝前撞向兒子滑板車尾輪，受傷倒地不起，一度昏迷。本報記者昨聯同前單車港隊代表、現單車教練仇多明實測新單車徑，發現五大安全隱患，包括女傷者撞中的防撞膠柱（見另稿）。仇表示南生圍至古洞一帶包括意外位置「陷阱處處」，老手亦可能會中招；記者昨日現場觀察，約一半騎車者沒戴頭盔。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20201003/s00002/1601661289045/%E5%9B%9B%E5%8F%A3%E5%AE%B6%E8%B8%A9%E5%B1%AF%E9%A6%AC%E6%96%B0%E5%96%AE%E8%BB%8A%E5%BE%91-%E6%AF%8D%E7%82%92%E8%BB%8A%E5%82%B7%E9%A0%AD-%E5%89%8D%E6%B8%AF%E9%9A%8A%E8%BB%8A%E6%89%8B-%E9%99%B7%E9%98%B1%E8%99%95%E8%99%95-%E8%80%81%E6%89%8B%E4%BA%A6%E6%9C%83%E4%B8%AD%E6%8B%9B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20201003%2Fs00002%2F1601661289045%2F%25E5%259B%259B%25E5%258F%25A3%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E8%25B8%25A9%25E5%25B1%25AF%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2596%25AE%25E8%25BB%258A%25E5%25BE%2591-%25E6%25AF%258D%25E7%2582%2592%25E8%25BB%258A%25E5%2582%25B7%25E9%25A0%25AD-%25E5%2589%258D%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%259A%258A%25E8%25BB%258A%25E6%2589%258B-%25E9%2599%25B7%25E9%2598%25B1%25E8%2599%2595%25E8%2599%2595-%25E8%2580%2581%25E6%2589%258B%25E4%25BA%25A6%25E6%259C%2583%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%258B%259B&d=eUEb8trTAlhqW9E3j8wil1IIeLT5oGwh5bXtaSRQp68%3D&h=100beb48\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20201003%2Fs00002%2F1601661289045%2F%25E5%259B%259B%25E5%258F%25A3%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E8%25B8%25A9%25E5%25B1%25AF%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2596%25AE%25E8%25BB%258A%25E5%25BE%2591-%25E6%25AF%258D%25E7%2582%2592%25E8%25